name: Harvest Low Volatility Canadian Equity Income ETF
longDescription: The fund achieves its objective by broadly owning Equity Securities of Canadian mid and large capitalization issuers directly, and (iv) further decreased volatility by writing covered call and/or covered put options on the securities in the Harvest Low Volatility Canadian Equity Income ETFs portfolio. The level of option writing may vary based on market volatility and other factors.
